      <title>特朗普政府要求最高法院停止教师赠款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-administration-asks-supreme-court-to-halt-teacher-grants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府要求美国最高法院许可，以扣留可能数亿美元的教师培训赠款，再次寻求紧急高等法院的帮助，以削减一项已建立的联邦支出计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-administration-asks-supreme-court-to-halt-teacher-grants</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 16:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在星期三立即准备自动关税公告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-prepares-auto-tariff-announcement-as-soon-as-wednesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们称，唐纳德·特朗普总统将在周三准备就其宣布有关自动税的公告，这一举动将在下周更广泛的关税推动下与全球贸易伙伴的战斗升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-prepares-auto-tariff-announcement-as-soon-as-wednesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 15:56:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>立陶宛的白俄罗斯边界附近的四名美国士兵失踪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/four-us-soldiers-go-missing-near-belarus-border-in-lithuania</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波罗的海国家的武装部队说，自周二以来，美国东部的四名军事人员和一辆车失踪了，当局正在当局进行搜救行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/four-us-soldiers-go-missing-near-belarus-border-in-lithuania</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 15:55:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及计划在关注工资，补贴时花费18％的支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/egypt-plans-18-spending-hike-with-eye-on-wages-subsidies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及将在下一个财政年度提高18％的支出，部分是为了扩大对最脆弱的支持，因为北非国家几十年来从其最严重的经济危机中出现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/egypt-plans-18-spending-hike-with-eye-on-wages-subsidies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 15:32:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bolsonaro要接受政变的审判，巴西的顶级法院小组规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/bolsonaro-to-stand-trial-on-coup-charges-top-court-panel-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西前总统杰尔·博尔森罗（Jair Bolsonaro）将在最高法院一致投票接受对他的刑事指控之后，将对他2022年大选后企图进行政变进行审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/bolsonaro-to-stand-trial-on-coup-charges-top-court-panel-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 15:29:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Gabbard承认敏感攻击计划已在聊天中分享</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/gabbard-says-no-classified-info-shared-as-chat-texts-published</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家情报局局长塔尔西·加巴德（Tulsi Gabbard）周三承认，在美国官员之间的一次聊天中，计划对也门的胡塞部队进行袭击的细节，这些官员无意间将包括新闻工作者包括在内。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/gabbard-says-no-classified-info-shared-as-chat-texts-published</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 14:51:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国会大会说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/us-treasury-risks-payment-default-as-soon-as-august-cbo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会预算办公室警告说，如果立法者未能提高或中止债务限额，联邦政府可能会在八月的时间内用完足够的钱来按时支付所有账单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/us-treasury-risks-payment-default-as-soon-as-august-cbo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 14:03:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大西洋发布有关胡塞攻击的完整信号文本链</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/atlantic-releases-details-of-signal-text-chain-on-houthi-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大西洋发布了美国顶级官员之间关于信号的小组聊天的笔录，这是无意中的编辑，揭示了国防部长皮特·赫格斯（Pete Hegseth）如何分享时机和武器系统的细节，这些细节和武器系统被用于对也门激进分子的攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/atlantic-releases-details-of-signal-text-chain-on-houthi-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 13:05:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯公布了140亿英镑的包裹，以修复英国受虐的预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/reeves-says-labour-has-rebuilt-uk-headroom-to-9-9-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）宣布，在今年的增长预测被削减了一半之后，福利和政府支出一揽子福利和政府支出，以填补该国财务状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/reeves-says-labour-has-rebuilt-uk-headroom-to-9-9-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 12:50:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其市场稳定在特朗普赞美，艰难的中央银行谈话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/erdogan-gets-trump-praise-amid-crackdown-that-s-rattled-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）认可他的对手泰耶普·埃尔多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan），而中央银行则承诺在需要时进一步收紧政策，而土耳其金融市场稳步稳步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/erdogan-gets-trump-praise-amid-crackdown-that-s-rattled-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 06:20:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
